Class World

  • java.lang.Object
    • ue5.World
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<Biome>

    public class World
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<Biome>
    This class provides a "World", which can store multiple numbers of Biomes. It has to have a name.

    Paul Jureschek, Michael Kinzkofer
